Collections.rule:
Individual: @A*
    Facts: hasName @E*
    Types: @A*(rdfs:label=["([A-Za-z]+)[0-9]+"]) 
    Facts: feedsWaterTo @C*
    Facts: hasChemicalStatus @H*(mm:prepend("ChemicalStatus")) 
    Facts: hasEcologicalStatus @G*(mm:prepend("EcologicalStatus")) 
    Facts: hasDegreeOfArtificiality @F*(mm:prepend("DegreeOfArtificiality"))
    Facts: hasPressure @J*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)
    Facts: hasPressure @K*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)
    Facts: hasPressure @L*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)
    Facts: hasPressure @M*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)
    Facts: hasPressure @N*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)

Individual: @A14
    Types: GroundWaterBody
    Facts: hasChemicalStatus ChemicalStatusGood
    Facts: hasQuantitativeStatus QuantitativeStatusGood
    Facts: hasName @E14

Individual: @A2
    Types: GroundWaterBody
    Facts: feedsWaterTo @C2, feedsWaterTo @C3, feedsWaterTo @C4, feedsWaterTo @C5
    Facts: feedsWaterTo @C6, feedsWaterTo  @C7, feedsWaterTo  @C8, feedsWaterTo  @C9
    Facts: feedsWaterTo @C10, feedsWaterTo  @C11, feedsWaterTo  @C12, feedsWaterTo  @C13
    Facts: hasChemicalStatus ChemicalStatusBad, hasQuantitativeStatus QuantitativeStatusGood
    Facts: hasName @E2
    Facts: hasPressure PressureDiffusePollution
